articles.title: Funko Pop confirms the New Title of Tom Hiddleston's Loki - CBR - Comic Book Resources
articles.description: Marvel Studios seemingly confirms the new title of Tom Hiddleston’s Loki in the form of a brand-new Funko Pop! Loki figure.
articles.content:
Tom Hiddleston’s Loki received a brand-new Funko Pop!, confirming the fan-favorite character’s new title in the Marvel Cinematic Universe.
